  "id": "RAW_4a8fc4d7",
  "title": "一边烧钱，一边裁员，扎克伯格没有二选一",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691565793&idx=1&sn=e34c43b9ec6af4a7ea0b7cbf8503b370",
  "date": "2026-03-14 07:04:00",
  "author": "腾讯科技",
  "siteName": "腾讯科技",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"2\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5458333333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;aspect-ratio:1.83143 / 1;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:6px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"307\" data-imgfileid=\"544082142\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8d73c15a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FQmK3dYQtkw3DFxn3R6UgibePsXsiadK0EVdDicObe6Fpp5icpgqAZb0k1zic9J7uRv3ibwX6zStb99DwEF7smemLWDXdItlVQzibTCp9EtMUkWp5Gw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(153, 153, 153);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.5px;display:block;font-size:12px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">扎克伯格计划裁员。图片由AI生成</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">文丨苏扬</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">编辑丨徐青阳</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">硅谷可能又要迎来一轮大裁员。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">近日，路透社援引多位知情人士的话称，Meta正在酝酿新一轮裁员，受影响员工比例可能达到20%或更多。如果数字确定，这将是该公司自2022年底启动重组以来力度最大的一次人员精简。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">截至去年12月31日，Meta员工总数近7.9万人。如果最终按20%的比例推进裁员，意味着将有1.6万人受到影响。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Meta此前已经进行了两轮大规模裁员，2022年11月裁减了约1.1万人，占当时员工总数的13%，四个月后又宣布再裁1万人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上述知情人士还透露，高层管理人员近期已向内部传达了这一意向，要求各团队开始规划如何精简人员。目前，裁员的具体时间点和最终规模尚未确定，Meta方面也未对此作出回应。</span></span></p>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">01&nbsp;</span></span></h1>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">AI太烧钱了</span></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">过去一年，扎克伯格一直在推动Meta更积极地参与</span></span><span dt-eid=\"em_huaci\" dt-params=\"huaci_type=ai&amp;huaci_name=生成式AI\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">生成式AI的竞争。为了吸引顶尖人才加入新组建的超级智能团队，Meta开出了相当丰厚的薪酬待遇。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">《纽约时报》援引知情人士所给信息显示，部分核心员工四年期的薪酬合同总值达到数亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"border:0px;vertical-align:middle;width:100%;max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;display:inline-block;aspect-ratio:1.49766 / 1;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"544082136\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=164cbe17&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FQmK3dYQtkw3slkvWt3nEIEQqP6RePakxz06LTEibJd03IOgkOBmSejjhDwMAvAUAadg1UXzRPKORFcEzE4bE6Shkqz5HwxmyHvovHwHCu3bY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除了人才，基础设施方面的投入更为庞大。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Meta此前表示，计划到2028年投入6000亿美元用于数据中心建设。本月早些时候，该公司收购了面向AI智能体的社交网络平台Moltbook。另外，Meta还在洽谈收购中国AI初创公司</span></span><span dt-eid=\"em_huaci\" dt-params=\"huaci_type=ai&amp;huaci_name=Manus\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Manus，交易金额至少20亿美元。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2026年1月，Meta预计全年支出将达1350亿美元，几乎是去年720亿美元的两倍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">面对如此庞大的开支，扎克伯格曾在1月的投资者电话会议中提到，已经开始看到“过去需要大团队的项目，现在由一位非常有才华的个人就能完成”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这番表态在一定程度上解释了公司对人力效率的重新审视：如果AI工具能让单人产出大幅提升，那么人员规模自然需要重新评估。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Meta的收缩裁员做法并非孤例。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">今年1月，亚马逊确认裁员约1.6万人，占员工总数近10%。上个月，金融科技公司Block裁减了近半员工，CEO杰克·多西（Jack Dorsey）提到，AI工具能力的提升让公司可以用更小的团队完成更多工作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对科技行业来说，重金投入AI，再通过AI提升人效、压缩人力成本，正在成为一种新的经营逻辑。</span></span></p>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">02&nbsp;</span></span></h1>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">新模型还是不乐观</span></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">模型的进展已经成为Meta的关键挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">去年，Meta的</span></span><span dt-eid=\"em_huaci\" dt-params=\"huaci_type=ai&amp;huaci_name=Llama 4模型\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Llama 4模型遭遇了一系列挫折，包括因早期版本的测试基准提供误导性结果而受到外界批评。Meta最终放弃了原定于夏季发布的该模型最大版本“Behemoth”。此后，超级智能团队开始着力开发一款名为“牛油果（Avocado）”的新模型，希望借此重振公司的技术地位。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">知情人士向《纽约时报》透露，</span></span><span dt-eid=\"em_huaci\" dt-params=\"huaci_type=ai&amp;huaci_name=牛油果模型\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">牛油果模型在内部测试中的表现仍未达到预期。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然相比上一代模型有明显提升，也好于谷歌去年3月发布的Gemini 2.5版本，但在推理、编码、写作等关键能力上，仍落后于谷歌去年11月发布的</span></span><span dt-eid=\"em_huaci\" dt-params=\"huaci_type=ai&amp;huaci_name=Gemini 3.0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini 3.0，与OpenAI、Anthropic等竞争对手的领先模型相比也存在差距。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">受此影响，Meta已经将牛油果模型的发布计划从3月推迟至5月。知情人士还提到，公司AI部门的负责人曾讨论过临时授权使用谷歌的Gemini来驱动自家AI产品，不过尚未作出最终决定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这一局面让公司的处境变得有些微妙。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一方面，巨额资金已经投下去，数据中心在建，人才高薪引进；另一方面，核心产品的竞争力尚未达到预期，无法快速转化为业务优势。</span></span></p>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">03&nbsp;</span></span></h1>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">团队内部“打架”</span></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">新模型的推进过程中，Meta AI团队本身也不稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">为了加强AI研发能力，Meta去年向初创公司Scale AI投资143亿美元，并让其首席执行官汪韬（Alexandr Wang）出任公司首席AI官。汪韬随后在内部组建了精英研究团队“</span></span><span dt-eid=\"em_huaci\" dt-params=\"huaci_type=ai&amp;huaci_name=TBD Lab\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">TBD Lab”，专注于新模型开发，团队规模约100人。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">《纽约时报》援引知情人士的话称，在牛油果模型发布前，已有少数研究人员离开团队。同时，汪韬与Meta首席产品官克里斯·考克斯（Chris Cox）、首席技术官安德鲁·博斯沃思（Andrew Bosworth）之间，也就新AI模型如何更好地服务于公司广告业务产生过分歧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">技术团队与业务团队之间的不同视角，在资源投入方向和应用落地上需要时间磨合。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上周，Meta在一份内部备忘录中表示，将在博斯沃思的部门下组建一个新的AI工程团队，与汪韬及其团队协作。此举被视为协调内部资源、推动项目落地的尝试。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">外界一度传出汪韬与扎克伯格关系紧张的说法，但Meta方面迅速予以否认，称这一说法“完全不实”。扎克伯格周一还在Threads上发布了一张与汪韬的合影，试图以轻松的方式平息外界猜测。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一边是持续投入的AI基础设施，一边是尚未达到预期的技术进展，再加上即将到来的人员调整，Meta正处在一个需要同时应对多重压力的关口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">据了解，其下一款模型已经定名为“西瓜（Watermelon）”，按照公司规划，将继续推进技术迭代。但在那之前，如何平衡投入与产出、技术与效率之间的关系，仍是Meta需要面对的重大挑战。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Meta 计划裁员 20%约 1.6 万人，同时巨额投资 AI 领域，面临 AI 烧钱、新模型竞争力不足、内部团队分歧等多重挑战，体现科技行业 AI 投资与人效压缩的新经营逻辑。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Meta 计划裁员 20%约 1.6 万人，同时巨额投资 AI 领域，面临 AI 烧钱、新模型竞争力不足、内部团队分歧等多重挑战，体现科技行业 AI 投资与人效压缩的新经营逻辑。",
  "summary": "本文报道了 Meta 正在酝酿的新一轮裁员计划，可能涉及 20%约 1.6 万名员工，这将是自 2022 年底以来最大规模的人员精简。文章分析了 Meta 面临的三重压力：第一，AI 太烧钱——为吸引顶尖人才开出数亿美元四年期薪酬合同，计划到 2028 年投入 6000 亿美元建设数据中心，2026 年预计支出 1350 亿美元；第二，新模型不乐观——Llama 4 受挫后，新模型牛油果在推理、编码、写作等关键能力上仍落后于 Gemini 3.0 和 OpenAI、Anthropic 的领先模型，发布时间已从 3 月推迟至 5 月；第三，团队内部不稳定——首席 AI 官汪韬与首席产品官、首席技术官在新模型如何服务广告业务上存在分歧，已有研究人员离开团队。文章指出，重金投入 AI 再通过 AI 提升人效、压缩人力成本，正在成为科技行业的新经营逻辑。",
